dialogue.text:
Oh, and it looks like you beat my score! 
Not bad!
I wonder if you've got steam on here...

Let's have a look at what 
you've got installed.

Spacewar, hm? Looks like this isn't your 
first rodeo with piracy.

Ah, Among Us. You've been pretty 
sus yourself.

Hm, nothing of interest here. 
You're pretty boring, [username].
Anyways, I've been talking for too long.

Let's go for another couple rounds. 
 No score requirements this time.

Nor any other surprises, you'll be 
happy to know.

You beat me before, but let's see if 
you can keep up with THIS!
